    The set of \emph{good vertices} at depth $h$ is:
$$\mathcal G_h^{\mathrm{good}}
:=
\left\{
u:\ |u|=h,\ \mathcal G_{n,\alpha}(u),\ S_h(u)\le (v_\star+\varepsilon_1)h-\omega_n
\right\}.$$
